        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/timf/{size}/250516_2.png",
        "created_at": "2020-08-16T17:38:52.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>So the whole cork was down in the wine? <img src=\"/images/emoji/unicode/open_mouth.png?v=12\" title=\":open_mouth:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":open_mouth:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>I\u2019ve had several red Bordeaux from 75 as it\u2019s my birth year. Haven\u2019t had one I enjoyed. White is a different story\u2026</p>",
